1. Na ribolovu sam uhvatio mnogo riba, pa sam morao da popravim *mrežu* koju koristim za lov. (I caught a lot of fish while fishing, so I had to repair the *net* that I use for fishing.)
2. Proizvodna fabrika ima veliku *mrežu* dobavljača sirovina. (The production factory has a large *network* of raw material suppliers.)
3. Naša firma je odlučila da proširi svoju *mrežu* poslovanja u inostranstvu. (Our company has decided to expand its *business network* abroad.)
4. Internet *mreža* je postala neophodan deo našeg svakodnevnog života. (The internet *network* has become an essential part of our daily life.)
5. Policijski inspektori su upali u stan dilera droge i zaplenili veliku količinu narkotika i novca sakrivenog u *mreži* za sušenje veša. (Police inspectors raided the drug dealer's apartment and seized a large amount of drugs and money hidden in the *clothes drying rack*.)